### 5 - Listar todos os usuários (admin)
GET {{baseURL}}/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 6 - Buscar usuário por ID (admin)
GET {{baseURL}}/users/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 7 - Atualizar usuário
PUT {{baseURL}}/users/2
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Maria Silva Atualizada",
  "email": "maria@email.com",
  "phone": "51977777777"
}

###

